import React from 'react'
import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'

function Footer() {
  return (
   
        <footer>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col className='text'>Copyrights @copy FONGANG BRICE</Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>

        </footer>
  
  )
}

export default Footer
